":"请教一下使用 VSCode 连接 WSL 开发，怎么将 WSL 中的端口号转发出来以在 win 下访问？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/940456","created":1684225063,"deleted":0,"content":"项目在 WSL 启动之后，监听 3000 端口，在宿主 win 中没法直接访问。\r\n```\r\nstarted server on 0.0.0.0:3000, url: http://localhost:3000\r\n```\r\n\r\n网上给出的解决方案是 Remote Explorer 中可以编辑端口映射，但是我并没有找到，\r\n\r\nControl Shift + P 搜索 Port 或者 Forward 关键字也没搜索到相关的。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n我记得之前连接到 docker container 中会有 port forward 的，是因为直接连 wsl 没这个功能？","content_rendered":"<p>项目在 WSL 启动之后，监听 3000 端口，在宿主 win 中没法直接访问。</p>\n<pre><code>started server on 0.0.0.0:3000, url: http://localhost:3000\n</code></pre>\n<p>网上给出的解决方案是 Remote Explorer 中可以编辑端口映射，但是我并没有找到，</p>\n<p>Control Shift + P 搜索 Port 或者 Forward 关键字也没搜索到相关的。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>我记得之前连接到 docker container 中会有 port forward 的，是因为直接连 wsl 没这个功能？</p>\n","last_modified":1684225063,"replies":18,"id":940456},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":55860,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8390,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":547027,"username":"Uahh","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Uahh","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"Uahh","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6491/dcab/547027_mini.png?m=1665633718","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6491/dcab/547027_normal.png?m=1665633718","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6491/dcab/547027_large.png?m=1665633718","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6491/dcab/547027_xlarge.png?m=1665633718","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6491/dcab/547027_xlarge.png?m=1665633718","created":1622610571,"last_modified":1665633718},"last_reply_by":"Breacher","last_touched":1684216425,"title":"2023 年入门 iOS 开发，请问有什么推荐的路径吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/940349","created":1684207472,"deleted":0,"content":"- 想开发个人软件，是直接上手 swift 吗，还会需要学习 OC 吗？\r\n- 如果我想把我的 web 应用(js/ts,html)包装成 app ，是可行的吗？\r\n- 入门有什么推荐的书或者文章视频吗？还是直接去读官方文档？  \r\n谢谢大家。","content_rendered":"<ul>\n<li>想开发个人软件，是直接上手 swift 吗，还会需要学习 OC 吗？</li>\n<li>如果我想把我的 web 应用(js/ts,html)包装成 app ，是可行的吗？</li>\n<li>入门有什么推荐的书或者文章视频吗？还是直接去读官方文档？<br/>\n谢谢大家。</li>\n</ul>\n","last_modified":1684207472,"replies":18,"id":940349},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":203153,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3800,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":274403,"username":"iblessyou","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/iblessyou","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e02b/ae05/274403_mini.png?m=1684201080","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e02b/ae05/274403_normal.png?m=1684201080","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e02b/ae05/274403_large.png?m=1684201080","created":1513216364,"last_modified":1684201080},"last_reply_by":"Mithril","last_touched":1684206128,"title":"老台式求推荐升级","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/940298","created":1684201868,"deleted":0,"content":"##### 老机器如下\r\n\ti3 4160\r\n    华擎（ ASRock ） B85M-HDS 主板（ Intel B85/LGA 1150)i3 4160\r\n    （ https://detail.zol.com.cn/356/355413/param.shtml  ）\r\n    350w 电源\r\n    DDR3 1600 4G*2\r\n    R7 260X 1G\r\n    1T 机械\r\n\r\n##### 查了下说明\r\n    存储扩展\r\n        PCI-E 标准\tPCI-E 3.0\r\n        PCI-E 插槽\t1×PCI-E X16 显卡插槽\r\n        1×PCI-E X1 插槽\r\n    存储接口\t4×SATA III 接口\r\n \r\n配置很低的老机器了，平时也就用来打些配置要求不高的网游啥的，偶尔会用来开发。\r\n使用量不太大，想给升级下体验，但因为主板限制，其实空间也不大。\r\n\r\n##### 需求\r\n- 希望买的东西，如果以后换机，也能用的，也就是说不为了匹配旧硬件强行买过时的东西。\r\n- 预算不限（但也别高到干脆整体换了）\r\n\r\n目前好像也就能换个固态，用来当系统盘，现在的机械就留着存些长期不动的东西吧。\r\n求个推荐，对 PCI-E 版本啊，带不带缓存有啥区别啊都不太了解。\r\n\r\n有其他可以优化体验的也可以。","content_rendered":"<h5>老机器如下</h5>\n<pre><code>i3 4160\n华擎（ ASRock ） B85M-HDS 主板（ Intel B85/LGA 1150)i3 4160\n（ https://detail.zol.com.cn/356/355413/param.shtml  ）\n350w 电源\nDDR3 1600 4G*2\nR7 260X 1G\n1T 机械\n</code></pre>\n<h5>查了下说明</h5>\n<pre><code>存储扩展\n    PCI-E 标准\tPCI-E 3.0\n    PCI-E 插槽\t1×PCI-E X16 显卡插槽\n    1×PCI-E X1 插槽\n存储接口\t4×SATA III 接口\n</code></pre>\n<p>配置很低的老机器了，平时也就用来打些配置要求不高的网游啥的，偶尔会用来开发。\n使用量不太大，想给升级下体验，但因为主板限制，其实空间也不大。</p>\n<h5>需求</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>希望买的东西，如果以后换机，也能用的，也就是说不为了匹配旧硬件强行买过时的东西。</li>\n<li>预算不限（但也别高到干脆整体换了）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>目前好像也就能换个固态，用来当系统盘，现在的机械就留着存些长期不动的东西吧。\n求个推荐，对 PCI-E 版本啊，带不带缓存有啥区别啊都不太了解。</p>\n<p>有其他可以优化体验的也可以。</p>\n","last_modified":1684201868,"replies":18,"id":940298},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":22221,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2580,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":297968,"username":"loxlblade","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/loxlblade","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4b07/efa8/297968_mini